data.name: Classic Tomato Basil Soup
data.quickTastyDescription: A warm and comforting classic, this Tomato Basil Soup is perfect for a cozy meal, packed with rich tomato flavor and fresh basil aroma.
detailedCookingInstructions: Heat olive oil in a large pot over medium heat.
Add chopped onion and garlic, saut√© until softened, about 5 minutes.
Pour in the canned diced tomatoes and vegetable broth, bringing to a boil.
Reduce heat and simmer for 15 minutes to let flavors meld.
Stir in fresh basil and sugar, then blend the soup until smooth using an immersion blender or a regular blender.
Return to heat, stir in heavy cream, and season with salt and black pepper to taste.
Serve warm with a drizzle of olive oil and additional basil if desired.
